gov.nasa.jpf.vm

Class Fields

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.jpf.vm.Fields
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArrayFields, NamedFields

    public abstract class Fields
extends Object
implements Cloneable
    Represents the variable, hash-collapsed pooled data associated with an object that is related to the object values (as opposed to synchronization ->Monitor). Contains the values of the fields, not their descriptors. Descriptors are represented by gov.nasa.jpf.vm.FieldInfo objects, which are stored in the ClassInfo structure.
    See Also:
    FieldInfo, Monitor
